Package items

Custom item objects created for Farm Simulator game Contains the structure for an item object and the unique constructors for the item subclasses. Item's function in game as consumables to boost daily actions. All items extend the FarmItem class, which is found in the farm package.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Alex Burling(arb142), Jonathon Howe(joh29)
See Also:
Item, Bonemeal, Brush, FeedBag, Fertiliser, Grain, Shampoo
